Package: fdagwr
Type: Package
Title: Functional Multi-Source Geographically Weighted Regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-06-11
Author: Andrea Enrico Franzoni [aut, cre], Alessandra Menafoglio [aut]
Maintainer: Andrea Enrico Franzoni <andreaenrico.franzoni@gmail.com>
Description: fdagwr fits Functional Weighted Regression (FWR) models, for 1D domains, constructing the respective predictors. Regression coefficients can be stationary and non-stationary, with at most two sources of non-stationarity. 
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.12), ggplot2, grid, gridExtra, viridis, patchwork, latex2exp
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
SystemRequirements: C++20, BLAS, LAPACK
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
